{"tid":1215390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子揮刀傷人 反斬甩自己手指頭","createTime":"2019-06-13T06:57:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T06:57:48.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4329842605a2774ef2f7b4e90ab48abf373b6e91","tid":1215390,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:57:48.000Z","msg":"黃大仙橫頭磡邨宏富樓對開發生傷人血案，下午接近2時，兩名男子發生爭執，其間一名男子揮刀斬向對方，對方左手上臂受傷，仍負傷反抗，與疑兇糾纏期間，疑兇反斬甩自己右手指一節指頭，不支倒地。警員接報到場，當場拘捕疑兇，與被斬男事主俱送院治理，警方正調查事件。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190613/59710821\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190613%2F59710821&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWPS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=528f13ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190613%2F59710821&h=01d98e50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190613/59710821</a>"}]}